title: BODY FOUND AT CALHOUN COUNTY GAS STATION
content: 04:12 PM CDT   Copyright by WIAT - All rights reserved   CALHOUN COUNTY SHERIFFS DEPARTMENT WAS CALLED OUT TO RJ GAS STATION ON HIGHWAY 431 BETWEEN ANNISTON AND GADSDEN THIS MORNING. CORONER PAT BROWN SAYS THAT A BODY THEY FOUND A FEMALE POSSIBLY IN HER LATE 20’S DEAD AT LOCATION. THEY PRONOUNCED HER DEAD AT 6AM THIS MORNING. CALHOUN COUNTY SHERIFF INVESTIGATION ARE WORKING THIS AS A HOMICIDE. THE CORONER IS WORKING TO ID WOMAN. THE INVESTIGATION IS STILL UNDERWAY. WILL UPDATE FURTHER INFORMATION.
